{"tid":1998063,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"應承我 大家要幫藍店渡過嚟緊兩個難關 手足唔係condom","createTime":"2020-05-02T06:27:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-02T08:10:25.000Z","uid":125168,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f33b4946081d0a613d6be01184bf9c051faaa02e","tid":1998063,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T06:27:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">手足想靠節日翻身，唔好再騎劫<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1. 5月10號老母節：</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gXFbC84.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgXFbC84.jpg&h=d922cb2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n仲可以去黃店黃酒樓富東閣食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2. 好多傻已經預售緊，當買coupon撐住黃店現金流都好:</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FMyc63K.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFMyc63K.jpg&h=601762c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/78giiau.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F78giiau.jpg&h=33d66c7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fEdpdJQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfEdpdJQ.jpg&h=5e4989b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1xPsbvw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1xPsbvw.jpg&h=28152696&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/51Y8FoS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F51Y8FoS.jpg&h=5888add8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dQykwvy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdQykwvy.jpg&h=faf65e02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iRdsVXd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiRdsVXd.jpg&h=7b569e2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一定要送手足最後一程<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"441fac03b93ff640d9864f2bd2984850bc90f011","tid":1998063,"uid":125168,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T06:27:17.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">少數霸權法則：當轉換選擇所花費既成本低時，最「堅持」既少數派係足以決定所有既人既行為模式</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n例子：點解飛機餐好少會有花生？<br />\n有嚴重花生敏感既人屬少數，大部份人其實都係食得花生<br />\n點解要因為遷就少數而犧牲大部份人喺飛機上食花生既權利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為大部份人覺得飛機上唔食花生都無所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（唔食花生＝低成本選擇）<br />\n航空公司為免麻煩，乾脆唔提供任何花生製品<br />\n結論：少數人有花生敏感，卻迫到大部份正常人唔可以喺飛機食花生<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n間唔中一家大細或者同朋友出外食飯，同行總會有中立同藍絲，特別係廢老<br />\n對呢班唔知頭唔知路既人黎講，食咩餐廳都無所謂<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">只要喺群體出外食飯時，一兩個硬頸黃絲堅持非黃絲餐廳不去（當然唔洗講出口話餐廳要係黃）<br />\n咁就可以令同行藍絲同中立都局住要食「黃金經濟圈」</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家可以再推想，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>如果每一個群體中，都有少量硬頸黃絲堅持唔幫襯藍絲企業，就足以令到社會中大部份群體都唔幫襯藍絲</strong></span><br />\n呢個就係少數硬頸撚如何取得絕對霸權既方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（當然黃絲係多數派，但呢到想講既係，唔需要好多人參與，就可以改變大部份人既行為模式）<br />\n<br />\n其他例子：一大班人出街行街時，堅持唔去港鐵旗下商場<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有好多應用例子，大家可以brainstorm一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n延伸閱讀：<br />\n<a href=\"https://medium.com/incerto/the-most-intolerant-wins-the-dictatorship-of-the-small-minority-3f1f83ce4e15\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedium.com%2Fincerto%2Fthe-most-intolerant-wins-the-dictatorship-of-the-small-minority-3f1f83ce4e15&d=eQX%2BqlmYp67lP1AM6ayufcorGdVmFuHsJRpnpeioS7U%3D&h=1dd69df5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://medium.com/incerto/the-most-intolerant-wins-the-dictatorship-of-the-small-minority-3f1f83ce4e15</a><br />\n<br />\nSource:［科普］少數霸權法則：迫到中立同藍絲都加入「黃金經濟圈」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1679102\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1679102</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"79a3b66de22f5360c464d7f38ae17bb41dcbdcb1","tid":1998063,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T06:29:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c33afac3c81d7e7fcf69fcbfc8f4a531be2445f7","tid":1998063,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T06:30:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oK4DicU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoK4DicU.png&h=8c4aa17e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n店主超黃"},{"pid":"42b9a51495728204e21b42e658174fc64ddedfc7","tid":1998063,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c33afac3c81d7e7fcf69fcbfc8f4a531be2445f7","tid":1998063,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T06:30:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oK4DicU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoK4DicU.png&h=8c4aa17e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n店主超黃"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T06:31:51.000Z","msg":"睇番黃金周category個堆網店都好多選擇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8629a4f02babdaf2f84be71f3ed253a5c735bccc","tid":1998063,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T06:32:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36e9994fd3e569ad493fed22ae4a11a0a87c2740","tid":1998063,"uid":340040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T06:39:42.000Z","msg":"好